{"tid":2133494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DQ 點解唔出Plan B? 根本唔合邏輯","createTime":"2020-07-31T06:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T08:43:03.000Z","uid":6777,"like":73,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"0afec04c8b03927a7fb6ced180e3c724196ee2af","tid":2133494,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T06:14:31.000Z","msg":"不嬲初選前都知會有dq 架啦<br />\n甚至一開始叫人登記選民，搞功能組果陣，你都知個game 係唔公平兼會比人dq<br />\n<br />\n玩得呢個game 就應該要plan bcde 都玩<br />\n最好幾百人參選<br />\n<br />\n到呢刻比人dq 先話唔玩？<br />\n不嬲參選你就已經有心理準備係港共既體制下抗爭，唔係點會咁大力搞功能組呀？<br />\n<br />\n而家先黎話唔派plan b, 咁樣根本係前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n部分人d 諗法本身都有衝突<br />\n<br />\n本身大搞35+就係要玩殘個體制<br />\n<br />\n最好幾百人去做plan b<br />\n等佢慢慢dq<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"x-small\">不過唔排除玩緊口術，等港共唔知有咩plan b 報左</span></span>"},{"pid":"eb29556b785307481b9ad70911e7cc701e01ce03","tid":2133494,"uid":6777,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"太少post 講 呢樣野<br />\n勁多post 叫人唔好plan b, 去其他線<br />\n<br />\n根本就唔合理<br />\n不嬲其他線都玩緊<br />\n點解要放棄呢條"},{"pid":"d5ffe8dac75d23be2de1024d89ddff76744b2883","tid":2133494,"uid":179718,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"無人選 = 少數派當選<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"24ac21829dc72a6cb980d99bdcf014e84ebc7c48","tid":2133494,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T06:24:47.000Z","msg":"人哋收集緊提名 今日入表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd9d38794e8944a9b6258e9fe78424a219450e1","tid":2133494,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"好似做緊"},{"pid":"e4f76ea72a3ddfe59ab3e55b8c2791b59bb5e421","tid":2133494,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9185c02efe8acb42889e529654895d261fd1e2aa","tid":2133494,"uid":6777,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24ac